Dear Applicant,

We are delighted to offer you admission to the Master of Science in Data
Engineering at Technische Universität Berlin, commencing Winter Semester
2026/27.

Programme Details:
- Degree: M.Sc. Data Engineering
- Start Date: October 1, 2026
- Duration: 2 years (4 semesters)
- Language of Instruction: English
- Tuition: EUR 334/semester (semester contribution fee only)

Scholarship Opportunity:
You are also eligible to apply for the DAAD Scholarship (full funding
including living expenses EUR 934/month). DAAD deadline: May 31, 2026.
Apply: https://daad.de/scholarships/phds-and-researchers/daad-scholarship

Acceptance Requirements:
- Confirm your admission by May 15, 2026 via online portal
- Submit certified official transcripts by June 30, 2026
- Proof of English proficiency (IELTS 7.0 or TOEFL 100+)
- Health insurance verification

Admission Portal: https://tu.berlin/en/study/admission/portal
General info: https://tu.berlin/dataengineering

Contact: admissions@tu.berlin.de | +49-30-314-23456

We look forward to welcoming you to TU Berlin!

Office of International Admissions
Technische Universität Berlin
